@page "/"
<PageTitle>About</PageTitle>

<div class="container py-5">
    <h1 class="display-4 text-center mb-4">About the Project</h1>

    <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-md-8">
            <p class="lead text-center">
                This project will serve as an online calculator that evaluates if a university has reached its
                Sustainable Development Goals (SDGs).
            </p>

            <div class="card shadow-lg">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title text-primary">What are Sustainable Development Goals?</h5>
                    <p>
                        The United Nations Sustainable Development Goals (SDGs) are a collection of 17 global goals
                        designed to be a "blueprint to achieve a better and more sustainable future for all" by 2030.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <hr />

            <h4 class="mt-4">Our Goal</h4>
            <p>
                Our goal is to create an accessible and user-friendly tool for university administrators and stakeholders
                to easily evaluate and track their progress toward achieving these important goals.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
